Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the WORK FORCE ADJUSTMENT DIRECTIVE AMENDMENT ORDER which
amends section 6.1.1 of the Directive so that employees declared surplus as
a result of privatization are guaranteed an offer of employment within the
Public Service, effective July 15, 1995.
